  "designMd": "# Hybrid Design System — Generated by Ditto\n\n> Blended from 2 inspirations\n> Generated on April 9, 2026\n\n## Inspirations\n- [Slack | Piattaforma di lavoro basata sull'IA e strumenti di produttività](https://slack.com/intl/it-it) — weight: 50%\n- [Maxima Therapy | Personalized Support for Neurodivergent Individuals](https://maximatherapy.com/) — weight: 50%\n\n## Mood Profile\n- **Tono**: Giocoso (-0.3)\n- **Formalità**: Bilanciato (-0.2)\n- **Energia**: Bilanciato (+0.0)\n- **Temperatura**: Caldo (-0.4)\n- **Densità**: Arioso (-0.4)\n- **Forma**: Morbido (-0.4)\n- **Profondità**: Bilanciato (-0.2)\n- **Palette**: Bilanciato (+0.0)\n- **Tipografia**: Espressiva (-0.3)\n- **Movimento**: Bilanciato (+0.2)\n\n## Font Setup\n\n### Fonts Used\n- **Heading**: `Salesforce-Sans`\n- **Body**: `Salesforce-Avant-Garde`\n- **Mono**: `ui-monospace`\n\n### CSS Custom Properties\n```css\n:root {\n  --font-heading: 'Salesforce-Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  --font-body: 'Salesforce-Avant-Garde', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  --font-mono: 'ui-monospace', ui-monospace, monospace;\n  --font-weight-heading: 600;\n  --font-weight-body: 400;\n}\n```\n\n## Color Palette & Roles\n\n### Primary\n- **Primary** (`#175a45`): CTAs, interactive elements, brand moments\n- **Secondary** (`#ca6784`): Supporting accents\n- **Accent** (`#727678`): Decorative highlights\n\n### Surfaces\n- **Background** (`#ffffff`): Page background\n- **Surface** (`#f4ede4`): Cards, elevated elements\n\n### Text\n- **Primary** (`#000000`): Headings, strong labels\n- **Secondary** (`#b35735`): Body text, descriptions\n- **Muted** (`#1c66d0`): Placeholders, captions\n\n### Semantic\n- **Border** (`#f6eef0`): Dividers, container borders\n- **Success** (`#22c55e`): Confirmations\n- **Warning** (`#f59e0b`): Caution states\n- **Error** (`#ef4444`): Destructive actions\n\n## Typography Rules\n\n| Role | Font | Weight | Notes |\n|------|------|--------|-------|\n| Display | Salesforce-Sans | 600 | Hero headlines |\n| Heading | Salesforce-Sans | 600 | Section titles |\n| Body | Salesforce-Avant-Garde | 400 | Standard text |\n| Mono | ui-monospace | 400 | Code, technical |\n\n## Component Stylings\n\n### Buttons\n**Primary**\n- Background: `#175a45`\n- Text: `#ffffff`\n- Padding: 9px 18px\n- Radius: 15px\n\n**Secondary**\n- Background: transparent\n- Text: `#175a45`\n- Border: 1px solid `#f6eef0`\n- Radius: 15px\n\n### Cards\n- Background: `#f4ede4`\n- Border: 1px solid `#f6eef0`\n- Radius: 23px\n- Shadow: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px`\n\n### Inputs\n- Background: `#ffffff`\n- Border: 1px solid `#f6eef0`\n- Radius: 15px\n- Focus: 1px solid `#175a45`\n\n## Layout Principles\n\n### Spacing Scale\n- XS: 4px, SM: 9px, MD: 18px\n- LG: 26px, XL: 35px, 2XL: 53px\n\n### Border Radius\n- Small: 8px\n- Medium: 15px\n- Large: 23px\n- Full: 9999px\n\n### Shadows\n- SM: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 0px 32px 0px`\n- MD: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px`\n- LG: `rgb(97, 31, 105) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset`\n\n## Design Decisions (from Mood Profile)\n\n- **Subtle depth**: Moderate shadows for gentle elevation\n- **Soft shapes**: Rounded corners, friendly feel\n- **Balanced spacing**: Standard rhythm between elements\n- **Medium headlines**: Clear hierarchy without overwhelming\n\n## Agent Prompt Guide\n\n### Quick Reference\n- Primary: `#175a45`, Background: `#ffffff`\n- Heading: Salesforce-Sans @ 600, Body: Salesforce-Avant-Garde @ 400\n- Radius: 8px / 15px / 23px\n- Spacing: 4px / 9px / 18px / 26px\n\n### CSS Variables (ready to paste)\n```css\n:root {\n  --color-primary: #175a45;\n  --color-secondary: #ca6784;\n  --color-accent: #727678;\n  --color-bg: #ffffff;\n  --color-surface: #f4ede4;\n  --color-text: #000000;\n  --color-text-secondary: #b35735;\n  --color-text-muted: #1c66d0;\n  --color-border: #f6eef0;\n  --color-success: #22c55e;\n  --color-warning: #f59e0b;\n  --color-error: #ef4444;\n  --radius-sm: 8px;\n  --radius-md: 15px;\n  --radius-lg: 23px;\n  --shadow-sm: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 0px 32px 0px;\n  --shadow-md: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) 0px 1px 10px 0px;\n  --shadow-lg: rgb(97, 31, 105) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset;\n}\n```\n",
